<br>
I personally whent with 50/50/28 because I want to be completely offensive. Once the parry bug is fixed, I can get Mastery of Parry and bring it up, along with adding +11 from items and +2 (or more) from realm ranks. That would mean at RR5, i'd get +15 from items/realmrank and 12 points from Mastery of Parry 1 and 2 (one mastery of is considered six points worth trained). That brings it to 55 parry. Not to shabby.<br>
<br>
